
# CodeCraft Studio 

##  Project Overview

CodeCraft Studio is a responsive multi-page website developed using **Bootstrap 5** as part of an internship task.  

The objective of this project was to explore and implement official Bootstrap components to build clean, responsive, and reusable UI layouts.

---

##  Task Requirements Covered

✔ Use Bootstrap 5 via CDN  
✔ Create 3 pages (Home, About, Contact)  
✔ Use official Bootstrap components  
✔ Maintain responsive design  
✔ Deploy using GitHub Pages  

---

##  Project Structure



---

##  Pages Description

### 1 Home Page
- Responsive Navbar
- Hero Section
- Services Section using Cards
- Footer

### 2 About Page
- Project description
- List Group component
- Responsive Grid layout

### 3 Contact Page
- Working contact form
- Bootstrap form components
- Responsive layout

---

##  Technologies Used

- HTML5
- Bootstrap 5 (CDN)
- Bootstrap Grid System
- Bootstrap Utility Classes

---

##  Responsiveness

This website is fully responsive and works properly on:

- Desktop
- Tablet
- Mobile devices

Bootstrap's grid system and utility classes were used to ensure proper responsiveness.

